headline: AFL Q4 Deep Dive: Product Refreshes and Distribution Expansion Drive Mixed Segment Trends
summary: Supplemental insurance provider Aflac (NYSE:AFL) missed Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q4 CY2025, with sales flat year on year at $4.28 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.57 per share was 7.3% below analysts’ consensus estimates.
